# Tailwind Conventions

## Class Organization

Order classes consistently:
1. Layout (display, position, flex/grid)
2. Spacing (margin, padding)
3. Sizing (width, height)
4. Typography (font, text)
5. Visual (bg, border, shadow)
6. Interactive (hover, focus)

```tsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 w-full text-sm bg-white border rounded-lg hover:shadow-md">
```

## Responsive Design

Mobile-first approach:
```tsx
<div className="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3">
```

## Dark Mode

```tsx
<div className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
```

## Custom Classes (cn utility)

```typescript
import { clsx, type ClassValue } from 'clsx';
import { twMerge } from 'tailwind-merge';

export function cn(...inputs: ClassValue[]) {
  return twMerge(clsx(inputs));
}

// Usage
<button className={cn(
  "px-4 py-2 rounded",
  isActive && "bg-blue-500",
  disabled && "opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed"
)}>
```

## Layout Patterns

### CSS Grid Dashboard
```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
  {cards.map(card => <Card key={card.id} {...card} />)}
</div>
```

### Sidebar Layout
```tsx
<div className="flex min-h-screen">
  <aside className="w-64 shrink-0 border-r">Sidebar</aside>
  <main className="flex-1 p-6">Content</main>
</div>
```

### Form Layout
```tsx
<form className="space-y-4 max-w-md">
  <div className="space-y-2">
    <label className="block text-sm font-medium">Email</label>
    <input className="w-full px-3 py-2 border rounded-md" />
  </div>
</form>
```

### Centered Content
```tsx
<div className="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
  <div className="max-w-md w-full p-6">Centered box</div>
</div>
```

## Rules

- Use Tailwind utilities over custom CSS
- Extract repeated patterns to components
- Use `@apply` sparingly (prefer component extraction)
- Maintain consistent spacing scale
